token_info.name: Vivid Spiral
token_info.description: Artist: Matt Foreman - This piece was released as part of Simulacra Two, a WebXR digital art menagerie created by REM5 Studios. Simulacra Two opened for a limited time beginning May 13, 2021 to provide a social space for Minnesota-based artists and their community to share and engage with their work, and make NFTs accessible to both the artists and collectors. More info can be found at rem5forgood.com/simulacratwo.
